title: Khloe Kardashian Rocks Lacy Thigh-High Boots, Huge Diamond Ring on Date Night With Tristan Thompson
text: Khloe Kardashian Rocks Lacy Thigh-High Boots, Huge Diamond Ring on Date Night With Tristan Thompson by Alex Ungerman 6:09 PM PDT, March 19, 2017 Playing Khloe Kardashian Rocks Lacy Thigh-High Boots, Huge Diamond Ring on Date Night With Tristan Thompson Khloe Kardashian went all out for her weekend date night with Tristan Thompson! The reality star was spotted out at Ruth's Chris Steak House in Beverly Hills, California, with the Cleveland Cavaliers player, after his team's Saturday loss to the Los Angeles Clippers. Khloe paired an oversized zip-up jacket with lace-up thigh high boots and some serious diamonds on that finger. Photo: AKM-GSI Mar 18, 2017 at 11:54pm PDT Still, that's some serious hardware! Earlier this month, a source close to the couple told ET that things are really heating up between Khloe and Tristan, going so far as to say, "There could be an engagement this summer." WATCH: Khloe Kardashian Expecting a Proposal From Tristan Thompson? Source Says It Could Happen 'This Summer' Still, the source noted that marriage isn't something the 32-year-old Revenge Body star is stressing about. "Khloe doesn't need a title to make their relationship real and she doesn't want to mess up how perfect it is now," the source said. "She's already done the marriage thing [with now ex-husband Lamar Odom]. Getting engaged is not something she's sitting around stressing about. If it happens, it happens, but it's not something she's stressing about right now." Meanwhile, Khloe recently went all out for the pro baller's 26th birthday. Watch the video below for more.
